Package: joplin-note-node
Version: 2.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libicu-dev | libicu74 | libicu72 | libicu70 | libicu66
Maintainer: INNO LOTUS PTY LTD <packages@innolotus.com>
Description: Joplin NWP Note Node
 An NPS/NWP node that exposes a Joplin instance (via Web Clipper or
 Joplin Server) as a ComplexNode for AI agents. Supports querying
 notes, full-text search, and write-back actions (create/update/delete).
